.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170504214819&h=8e38216b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏身倒奶兼且派心心冧男友～<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/photo/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_06b.JPG?20170504214819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_06b.JPG%3F20170504214819&h=7d968b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係冇得頂呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/photo/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170504214819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170504214819&h=5703ed64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曹思詩仲好大方成日上載水着相派福利。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/photo/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_08b.jpg?20170504214819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20170504214819&h=b416e6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好索呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/photo/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_09b.jpg?20170504214819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20170504214819&h=3533838a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n難怪網友都話要力捧佢做無綫新一代「咪神」喇！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/photo/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_10b.jpg?20170504214819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20170504214819&h=c3904a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有網友封佢做「翻版唐詩詠」𠻹吖！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/photo/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_11b.jpg?20170504214819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_11b.jpg%3F20170504214819&h=42b52f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行山都不忘晒線～<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/photo/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_12b.jpg?20170504214819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001_12b.jpg%3F20170504214819&h=1aab8612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n贏晒喇！<br />\n<br />\n無綫人才輩出，咩類型嘅靚女都有，單單靠副靚樣未必成功上位，所以近年唔少無綫小花選擇喺節目性感上陣，務求喺芸芸小花中突「圍」而出，今次就輪到曹思詩彈出啦！曹思詩最近為無綫官方FACEBOOK專頁「SEE SEE TVB」拍攝短片，當中佢換上多件低胸衫，大騷32C激凸上圍，仲不時烏身倒奶，隨即成為網民熱話！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>床上擺甫無限遐想</strong><br />\n<br />\n片中所見，飾演麻煩女友嘅曹思詩做出唔少「港女」行為，包括無端端向男友發脾氣，唔識煮嘢食，仲要咩嘢事都可以慶祝一餐等，但相信大家嘅重點都唔係佢嘅演技上，而係身材囉！皆因着低胸短裙嘅曹思詩晒胸又晒腿，養眼程度爆燈，又好難叫人唔放錯焦點。鏡頭一轉，曹思詩換上小背心同熱褲，喺床上大擺性感甫士，認真令人無限遐想。之後佢仲嚟一招烏身倒奶，兼且派心心冧男友，就連鏡頭後嘅雄性動物都抵擋唔住，流住鼻血留言大讚佢「SUPER HOT」，仲話要力捧佢做無綫新一代「咪神」！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「翻版唐詩詠」</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢位潛力新「咪神」現年25歲，演出過唔少無綫劇集，不過都係做路人角色為主，就連近期熱播劇《全職沒女》都有佢份，直至早前主持節目《山系女行Yama Girl》而為人熟悉。另外，唔少網友都話曹思詩同絕世好女友唐詩詠好似樣，因而被封「翻版唐詩詠」。曹思詩仲好大方，經常喺社交網上載水着相派福利，就連行山都會性感打扮，所以唔講咁多，大家睇相啦！<br />\n<br />\n網民有話兒：<br />\nAraXXXHo：SUPER HOT!!!<br />\nXXXryLam：嘩！烏身倒奶呢招掂！<br />\nXXmmyChXX：估唔到佢身材咁好喎！<br />\nKaLXXX：條女熟口熟面，好似成日做路人甲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170504%2Fbkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001.html&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9cd8eb68\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170504/bkn-20170504193535388-0504_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e582b96fa439ec993e9cc27e7174a8f327334ac","tid":229793,"uid":72702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:55:26.000Z","msg":"除左都係有眼耳口鼻邊忽似唐詩詠？<br />\n除左對燈有乜咁正？"},{"pid":"fabe7c5484434b23b2c6fed8c9d119e4ffea501b","tid":229793,"uid":32015,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:56:40.000Z","msg":"好撚豬"},{"pid":"11cfc103966adc5b28d4684e6cf841064f5420d9","tid":229793,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a377f1811664b5adc40b606adc433df8092f3153","tid":229793,"uid":1685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左都係有眼耳口鼻邊忽似唐詩詠？<br />\n除左對燈有乜咁正？</blockquote><br />\n對燈都唔多正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85178c6eda9d3bbf9d79462da986a3bef43a8ecc","tid":229793,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:00:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3728dfde9a4b28e5d3bbd41abac8db4534b7b85a","tid":229793,"uid":18271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左都係有眼耳口鼻邊忽似唐詩詠？<br />\n除左對燈有乜咁正？</blockquote><br />\n咁都唔正平時食開咩女咁把炮"},{"pid":"e1ca22703ec66b60da431fe8a3bb5de68b68d8dc","tid":229793,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:04:34.000Z","msg":"得對奶<br />\n<br />\n個口唔知乜事， 啲牙明明齊 但好哨咁"},{"pid":"d2ec86b9a01ca0a243477accf1722dafc1ff9d9e","tid":229793,"uid":32722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"這麼醜的囡"},{"pid":"7c025ad21b0beaeec7151f8289f2dd0a95b65df7","tid":229793,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:08:36.000Z","msg":"呢條女咁多年都唔掂"},{"pid":"3dfca845a7327bbfd8c0beb4bf9ae4d6c42bce15","tid":229793,"uid":31611,"lik